  "title": "Security Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Served as the hotel compliance and enforcement officer</li>\n  <li>Patrol Hotels' compound, commercial premises and car park to prevent and detect signs of intrusion and ensure security of doors, windows, and gates</li>\n  <li>Write reports of daily activities and irregularities, such as equipment or property damage, theft, presence of unauthorized persons, or unusual occurrences</li>\n  <li>Screen and check the ID of all personnel entering the hotel</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidate must possess a valid Security license</li>\n  <li>At least 1 year of working experience in the related field.</li>\n  <li>Physically fit</li>\n  <li>Candidate with fire safety and first aid knowledge would be an added advantage</li>\n  <li>Able to work rotating shifts including weekends and public holidays</li>\n  <li>Served as the hotel compliance and enforcement officer</li>\n  <li>Patrol Hotels' compound, commercial premises and car park to prevent and detect signs of intrusion and ensure security of doors, windows, and gates</li>\n  <li>Write reports of daily activities and irregularities, such as equipment or property damage, theft, presence of unauthorized persons, or unusual occurrences</li>\n  <li>Screen and check the ID of all personnel entering the hotel</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
